<plot>Dark Legacy is a production in the tradition of the great masters of the genre, like Alfred Hitchcock, John Carpenter and not to forget Edgar Wallace, which understands itself as an experiment in Mystery &amp; Horror. After a sudden and tragic lost in the family, four relatives of the deceased met again when the last will should be announced. But the distrust of all could be felt in the room. The last will requires that all remained relatives have to spend the whole night on the belongings of deceased with his old lawyer. During that night they find a dark secret, which will have a great impact on there destiny. Some legacy should be turned down.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?127209</url></doc>
